data.description: Check out this fabulous home! NO HOA! Sellers are willing to give $10,000 to help buy down buyers interest rate or assist with closing cost if under contract by February 4th. Sellers are VERY motivated to sell. New roof, the foundation has been done under the entire house with 10 years transferable warranty, new fence, new 100% waterproof vinyl flooring throughout the entire house, all new kitchen appliances, touch screen refrigerator comes with the house, all new light fixtures in the interior and new interior paint. The owners have put plenty of love and great touches to this home to make it yours. This house features high vaulted ceilings with an open layout and plenty of space with 2 living areas, 2 dining areas, open study area or additional living area, oversized master bedroom with stand up shower and separate tub. Surrounded with plenty of shopping centers, restaurants and great schools. Schedule your showing today!
